dback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dqd1665702725479.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dqd1665702725479.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dqd1665702725479.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dqd1665702725479\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      field name size\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__field_name_size_145129\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the maximum size of field names.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__topic_d47672e1_d47673e1_d47674e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__d6798e17\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = field name size :</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldNameSize</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__d6798e29\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = fldnmsize :</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldNameSize</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__topic_d31157e1_d31158e1_d31159e1_d31160e1_d31161e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d639844e80\">\n                        \n Use\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Applies to</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Connector Syntax</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2 connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBC connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODx</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dqd1665702725479__table_d4493e1_d4494e1_d4495e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ODx_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__p_d47684e1_d47685e1_d47686e1\">There are no restrictions on use.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__topic_d31162e1_d31163e1_d31164e1_d31165e1_d31166e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d639844e176\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__p_d47690e1_d47691e1_d47692e1\">Use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">field name size</code> option to specify the maximum size, in number of characters, allowed for field names.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dqd1665702725479__p_d47693e1_d47694e1_d47695e1\">When specified, the connector truncates field names to the specified size. The minimum size is <code class=\"ph codeph\">8</code>; if a lower value is specified, no truncation occurs.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS field name size : 18</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526932\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526932\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "field name size Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 field name size Specify the maximum size of field names. USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = field name size : FieldNameSize USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = fldnmsize : FieldNameSize Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax DB2 connector DB2 USYS$DB2_PARAMS ODBC connector ODx USYS$ODx_PARAMS There are no restrictions on use. Description Use the field name size option to specify the maximum size, in number of characters, allowed for field names. When specified, the connector truncates field names to the specified size. The minimum size is 8 ; if a lower value is specified, no truncation occurs. USYS$DB2_PARAMS field name size : 18 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}